des:
avgeek News allows you to listen to the latest aviation news as well as analysis articles.

avgeek is an aviation news site which provides the latest updates in the aviation industry, as well as interesting insights into airlines and their operations.

Just say:

"Alexa, open avgeek News"
"Alexa, start avgeek News"
"Alexa, start avgeek News"
